headline: Pharma Stock Roundup: PFE's 2025 Outlook, MRK & ABBV's M&A Deals
summary: PFE issues its financial guidance for 2025. MRK and ABBV announce M&A deals. SNY/TEVA's IBD drug succeeds in a phase IIb study.
